<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.github.taskflow</id>
  <name>TaskFlow</name>
  <summary>A minimal kanban board for personal task management</summary>

  <description>
    <p>TaskFlow is a lightweight kanban-style task manager that helps you organize your work into columns: To Do, In Progress, and Done.</p>
    <p>Key features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Drag-and-drop cards between columns</li>
      <li>Keyboard shortcuts for power users</li>
      <li>Local storage — no account required</li>
      <li>Export and import boards as JSON</li>
    </ul>
    <p>TaskFlow is built for people who want a <em>simple</em> tool without the overhead of complex project management software.</p>
  </description>

